Package com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi

Class Core

java.lang.Object
org.bukkit.plugin.PluginBase
org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
com.github.freddyyj.localizationapi.Core
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandExecutor, TabCompleter, TabExecutor, Listener, Plugin
public class Core
extends JavaPlugin
implements Listener
Main class for LocalizationAPI. Extends JavaPlugin. Don't create this object manually.

Implements Listener to listen player join and quit event. Don't create this class manually. Use PluginManager.getPlugin(String) to get this object.

Author:
FreddyYJ_
